             was indicted for <rs id="t17740907-54-off270" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17740907-54-off270" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740907-54-off270" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing forty guineas in money, numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17740907-54-victim450" type="victimName">
                           Felix
                            Calvert
                        <interp inst="t17740907-54-victim450" type="surname" value="Calvert"></interp>
